    "description": "该模板是GameCreator官方出品的游戏模板-《星之瞳》。可用于可视化制作AVG、视觉小说等类型的游戏。<br>该模板包含了GameCreator引擎的功能以及模板独有的核心系统以及编辑器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >事件编辑器</h2>事件编辑器用于无编程、可视化的事件指令方式快捷制作游戏内容。<br>剧本和演出效果以及实时预览都在这里实现。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/9532abb7b3394c59957916be8e347d6a.poster.avif?t=1742054827\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/9532abb7b3394c59957916be8e347d6a.webm?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/9532abb7b3394c59957916be8e347d6a.mp4?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >镜头管理</h2>支持深度，通过镜头展现层次感。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/62e7595f9f5518608f7fa5f7c78d8b5e.poster.avif?t=1742054827\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/62e7595f9f5518608f7fa5f7c78d8b5e.webm?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/62e7595f9f5518608f7fa5f7c78d8b5e.mp4?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >材质特效</h2>支持材质Shader效果，高级开发者可以自定义。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/0fb4891b0f41a69c86ec3286a10dee5b.poster.avif?t=1742054827\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/0fb4891b0f41a69c86ec3286a10dee5b.webm?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180560/extras/0fb4891b0f41a69c86ec3286a10dee5b.mp4?t=1742054827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >此外还包含但不限于的内容如下</h2>立绘管理：方便地管理一个人物多个动作、帧数、部位<br>界面管理：可视化制作界面<br>视频支持：支持mp4、webm格式的视频<br>语音支持：剧本台词可以设置对应的语音文件<br>动画系统：支持序列帧动画和粒子动画<br>高级扩展：高级开发人员可以通过脚本和插件扩展内容<br>......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用该模板制作的部分游戏</h2>《日日夜夜》：<br>《记得我》：<br>《罪狱：soul》： <br>《重启：泡沫篇 Reboot:FROTH》：",
